135
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,240
It's not possible.

136
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,639
It can't be, right?

137
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,040
Is it a happy pulse?

138
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:49,600
Go away.

139
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,319
It's just heatstroke.

140
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:52,959
I'm telling you,

141
