Let's go home.

146
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:03,319
Let me give you a ride.

147
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,120
No need.

148
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:04,959
Let me tell you,

149
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,079
