174
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,040
My daughter will be here soon.

175
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,879
You young people have a good chat.

176
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,039
Mom.

177
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,480
When did I agree?

178
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:35,799
Don't go back on your word.

179
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:39,360
He's shy.

180
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,399
He's getting more handsome.

181
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,200
Dad.

182
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,120
I'm fine.

183
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,399
So soon?

184
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,519
Much better.

185
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,600
Let's go.

186
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,200
Go.

187
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:51,159
Let's go.

188
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:51,960
