193
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,639
Auntie,

194
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,279
I came with my dad.

195
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,120
That's good.

196
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,919
Today,

197
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:06,240
Xiaofei is going to meet a girl.

198
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:07,279
You can have dinner together.

199
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,080
He's too shy to be alone.

200
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:10,840
It's better to have more people.

201
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,559
Auntie, I don't feel well today.

202
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:13,720
I'm going back first.

203
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,240
What's wrong with you?

204
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:16,919
Heatstroke?

205
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:17,840
It's nothing.

206
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,360
So, this girl and Fei

207
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,080
are friends, huh?

208
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,080
Ma'am,

209
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:28,559
we're relatives. Don't worry.

210
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:29,919
Relatives?

211
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:32,200
Look at you.

212
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,480
I didn't think too much.

213
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,320
We'll be going now.

214
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,120
Let's go, Dad.

215
