237
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:26,639
I came here as soon as I knew.

238
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,960
It was arranged by my mom.

239
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,279
I didn't know about it.

240
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,039
You don't have to explain to me.

241
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,399
We broke up a long time ago.

242
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,759
And you have your own life.

243
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,159
Don't miss a good girl when you meet her.

244
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,600
I'll have to call her sister-in-law in the future.

245
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:46,639
Okay.

246
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,039
It doesn't matter.

247
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,000
I'll be more restrained in the future.

248
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,799
Stay away from you a bit.

249
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:56,159
Just endure the stomach pain.

250
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:57,559
Anyway, it won't kill me.

251
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,279
Take it.

252
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:14,879
I'm leaving now.

253
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,039
190 yuan.

254
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:19,799
Scan the code.

255
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:20,679
Thank you.
